# Shared helpers

Before adding streaming, polling, queue, or save logic, check `AGENTS.md` and use existing helpers.

## Must use

- **Client SSE:** `consumeHarnessSSE` from `@/lib/client/sse` — never inline `getReader` + `split('\n\n')`
- **API SSE:** `harnessSSEResponse` from `@/lib/api/sse` — never duplicate ReadableStream boilerplate
- **Queue PATCH:** `patchQueueAction` from `@/lib/client/queue`
- **Action labels:** `ACTION_TYPE_LABELS` from `@/lib/harness/action-labels` (not `queue.ts` in client code)
- **Work feed:** `useWorkFeed` + `WorkFeedProvider` from `@/hooks/useWorkFeed` (not ad-hoc `/api/tasks` polling)
- **Generic polling:** `usePollingFetch` from `@/hooks/usePollingFetch` — only when Work feed is not the consumer
- **Save panels:** `useSaveFeedback` from `@/hooks/useSaveFeedback`
- **KB batch write:** `writeManyKB` / `mergeProfile` — not manual profile merge loops
- **Agent overrides:** `resolveLibraryAgent` + `loadAgentOverrides` from `@/lib/agents/resolve`

## Do not restore

Legacy Dashboard, `useAgentSession`, `lib/orchestrator`, `lib/prompts/*`, imperative `lib/agents/leads/*`, or `ActionQueue.tsx`.

